# This environment currently creates only the shared VPC.

# Networking inputs now follow the topology defined in ../../modules/vpc.
# Default values already match the agreed 10.0.0.0/24 main CIDR and
# 100.64.0.0/23 pod CIDR design.
# Override cidr_block, subnet_cidrs, or pod_subnet_cidrs here only if your
# live environment uses values different from variables.tf defaults.

# Future example notes only:
# ECR / EKS / frontend hosting are intentionally not wired into prod/main.tf.
# If we add them back later, recover their input examples from Git history
# rather than enabling them directly from this file.
